data.description: Meticulously maintained 3 BR/2BA property in the heart of Sebastian!  Too many updates to mention.  Features include split floor plan, huge master bedroom, custom kitchen pantry, wood flooring in main living area, new screens on windows, front porch and lanai, new roof and gutters and 5-zone irrigation system in 2023, new A/C and septic drain field in 2021, new storage shed in 2022 and much more!  A must see! Room sizes approx. and subject to error.
